## 4K INTERFRAME NR
Select **ON** to enable interframe noise reduction.

| Options |     |
|---------|-----|
| ON      | OFF |

- Interframe noise reduction is available only when frame rates of **29.97P** or slower are selected at a frame size of **4K** or **DCI**.
